    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The default value for $noController is false for the direct method of the viewRenderer helper.  I think this should be null instead.</p>

<p>direct() proxies setRender which has the correct default value for $noController.</p>

<p>If I set noController to true in my boostrap, I shouldn't have to set the value again when calling $this-&gt;_helper-&gt;viewRender('script-name');</p>

